<p>
    Moreover, with a complete finite state machine model of the protocol, it became clear that there is some, previously
    unknown, communication backchannel between C&C master server and the spam template servers. These kinds of insights
    into the C&C structure and behaviour of sophisticated botnets like MegaD are made possible with the understanding of
    their protocols.
